# 我的 VIM 设置，reloaded

## Installation

    cd ~
    git clone https://github.com/lusijin/vimrc.git
    ln -s ~/vimrc/.vim .
    ln -s ~/vimrc/.vimrc .
    ln -s ~/vimrc/.gvimrc .
    
    #install vundle
    git clone https://github.com/gmarik/vundle.git ~/.vim/bundle/vundle
    
    vim
    #in your vim, run :BundleInstall
